Nutrient data for: TRIDENT SENSES GUM WATERMELON SUGAR FREE, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 05034660521082
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

INGREDIENTS: Sweeteners (sorbitol, maltitol, xylitol, maltitol syrup, aspartam, acesulfam K, sucralose), gum base, flavorings, humectant (E422), emulsifiers (sunflower lecithin, E472a), acids (E330, E296, E334), colours (E160c, E141), antioxidant (E321).
